item.title: CVE-2017-16152|2024-09-17T02:37:05.290Z -- hackerone -- static-html-server%20node%20module
item.description: static-html-server is a static file server. static-html-server is vulnerable to a directory traversal issue, giving an attacker access to the filesystem by placing "../" in the url.
